# Notes
  # A quick way to set unbreakable gear. Rework if needed for specific inventory items.

# Armour
item modify entity @s armor.head gc:set_unbreakable
item modify entity @s armor.chest gc:set_unbreakable
item modify entity @s armor.legs gc:set_unbreakable
item modify entity @s armor.feet gc:set_unbreakable

